Package com.example.releasefrontend.landlordScreens

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FillUnitArrayActivity
    Screen allowing landlord to repeatedly fill attributes of units for however many units were specified to be initialized in the given building
    InitializeBuildingActivity
    Base building intialization screen allowing landlord to intitialize the address and the number of units for a new building
    LandlordHomePageActivity
    Main splashscreen for a logged in landlord, allowing to see and post announcements and posts to the building community
    nav_landlord_activity
    Navigation drawer to be placed over all landlord screens.
    PropertyManagementActivity
    Main splashscreen for a logged in landlord, allowing to see their given properties and select them.
